    "macroSummary": "Market is rallying on hopes for U.S.-Iran diplomatic talks that could end the Middle East conflict, driving oil prices down and risk assets higher. Bitcoin has surged above $75K-76K on tame PPI inflation data and geopolitical de-escalation hopes, while traditional markets see broad-based gains with the Nasdaq approaching its 10th consecutive session of gains.",
