      "Maintain Maturity sector overweight but prepare for rotation if oil continues falling and growth concerns ease"
    ],
    "keySignals": [
      "Bitcoin above $75K signals strong risk-on sentiment and potential break of bear market structure if sustained.",
      "Oil falling on Iran talks reduces stagflation threat and removes key headwind for equity markets.",
      "Dollar weakness with declining oil correlation suggests Fed policy flexibility may be returning.",
      "Small business sentiment hitting post-Liberation Day lows contrasts with market optimism, signaling potential divergence."
